<!-- SECTION 7: 7-STEP PROCESS -->
<section class="steps-section" id="procedure-section">
    <div class="section-container">
        <header class="section-header" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Process</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">8 Steps to Convert Public Ltd to Pvt Ltd in Delhi</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle" style="text-align:left;max-width:100%;">Patron's Public-to-Private conversion pipeline runs from pre-conversion eligibility review through board resolution and EGM with special resolution at 75 percent majority, Form MGT-14 filing within 30 days under Section 117, Form INC-25A newspaper publication and Form INC-26 individual creditor notice with 21-day objection window, Form RD-1 application to the Regional Director (Northern Region) at Lok Nayak Bhawan within 60 days, RD hearing representation where objections received, RD order receipt and Form INC-28 filing with ROC within 15 days of the RD order. Each step is a fixed deliverable - no surprises mid-engagement.</p>
        </header>
        <div class="steps-container">
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <span class="step-badge">Step 1</span>
                    <h3 class="step-title">Pre-Conversion Eligibility Review</h3>
                    <p>Verify member count is under 200; confirm no outstanding public deposits; check Rule 41(5) clearance (no ongoing investigation, inspection or prosecution); map creditor and debenture holder universe for Form INC-26; for listed companies confirm SEBI delisting under SEBI Regulations 2021 is complete.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-visual">
                    <div class="step-illustration">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 200 180" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="30" y="35" width="140" height="120" rx="6" fill="#FFF" stroke="#14365F" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="45" y="50" width="50" height="32" rx="3" fill="#E8F5E9" stroke="#10B981" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="70" y="62" font-size="9" fill="#10B981" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">Public Ltd</text><text x="70" y="74" font-size="8" fill="#14365F" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">200+ members</text><text x="105" y="71" font-size="12" fill="#E8712C" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">&#8594;</text><rect x="115" y="50" width="50" height="32" rx="3" fill="#FFE5E5" stroke="#DC2626" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="140" y="62" font-size="9" fill="#DC2626" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">Pvt Ltd</text><text x="140" y="74" font-size="8" fill="#14365F" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">&lt;200 members</text><rect x="45" y="92" width="110" height="22" rx="3" fill="#FFF3E0" stroke="#E8712C" stroke-width="1"/><text x="100" y="106" font-size="9" fill="#E8712C" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">Sec 2(68) Cap</text><rect x="45" y="118" width="110" height="22" rx="3" fill="#F0F4F8" stroke="#14365F" stroke-width="1"/><text x="100" y="132" font-size="9" fill="#14365F" font-weight="700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Arial">Rule 41(5) Clear</text></svg>
