                    <p>Board passes resolution to convene EGM with 21 clear days notice under Section 101; EGM convened with explanatory statement under Section 102; special resolution passed at 75 percent majority altering MOA (name change to 'Private Limited') and AOA (incorporating Section 2(68) restrictions).</p>
                </div>
